ZH: 不要泼水到电子设备上，会造成损坏。
EN: Do not splash water on electronic devices, it will cause damage.

ZH: 他不小心把饮料泼在桌子上。
EN: He accidentally spilled his drink on the table.

ZH: 在暴雨中散步，很容易被泼湿。
EN: Walking in a storm, you are very likely to get splashed.

ZH: 她用手上的水泼了我一脸。
EN: She splashed me in the face with the water on her hand.

ZH: 请小心泼油，容易引发火灾。
EN: Be careful when splashing oil, it can easily cause a fire.

ZH: 她不慎将墨水泼到了自己的衬衫上。
EN: She accidentally spilled ink on her shirt.

ZH: 小心泼洒香水在皮肤上，可能会引起过敏。
EN: Be careful when splashing perfume on your skin, it may cause an allergic reaction.

ZH: 水手在岸上不小心将一桶水泼了出去。
EN: The sailor accidentally spilled a bucket of water on shore.

ZH: 别再泼水到我的花园里了，花都被淹死了。
EN: Stop splashing water into my garden, all the flowers are drowned.

ZH: 泼一点美白精华液在脸上，然后轻轻按摩。
EN: Splash a bit of whitening essence on your face and gently massage.

ZH: 我不小心将酱汁泼到了桌子上。
EN: I accidentally spilled sauce on the table.

ZH: 铲车不小心将水桶泼开了。
EN: The forklift accidentally tipped over the water bucket.

ZH: 泥浆喷泄出来，泼得他满脸全是泥巴。
EN: The mud spurted out, splashing mud all over his face.

ZH: 台风过后，路上积水很深，容易被泼湿。
EN: After the typhoon, there is deep water on the road that is easy to splash on.

ZH: 狗尾巴甩打了一下，泼了我一脸尘土。
EN: The dog wagged its tail and splashed me with dirt.

ZH: 孩子们在池塘边玩耍，水花四溅，到处都是泼水声。
EN: The children played by the pond, causing water to splash everywhere with the sound of splashing.

ZH: 圆珠笔不小心破了，墨水泼了一手。
EN: The pen accidentally broke, splashing ink all over my hand.

ZH: 他用食油泼在炸鸡上，使其更加香脆美味。
EN: He splashed cooking oil on the fried chicken to make it more crispy and delicious.

ZH: 他从头到脚被腳踏車泼了一身泥。
EN: He was splashed all over with mud from head to toe by a passing bicycle.
